{# hero.njk - Enhanced component with improved structure and JavaScript integration #}

<!-- Hero Section Start -->
<section
  id="hero"
  class="hero-bg relative flex items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-center overflow-hidden w-full h-screen pt-14 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:bg-gradient-to-br before:from-navy-900/85 before:to-navy-900/70 bg-[url('https://res.cloudinary.com/{{ site.cloudinaryCloudName }}/image/upload/w_640,h_480,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto,g_auto/cafe_pnkngz')] sm:bg-[url('https://res.cloudinary.com/{{ site.cloudinaryCloudName }}/image/upload/w_1024,h_600,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto,g_auto/cafe_pnkngz')] lg:bg-[url('https://res.cloudinary.com/{{ site.cloudinaryCloudName }}/image/upload/w_1920,h_1080,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto,g_auto/cafe_pnkngz')]"
  role="banner"
  aria-label="Seção principal do evento Café com Vendas"
  data-reveal
  data-cloudinary-bg="cafe_pnkngz"
>
  <!-- Decorative SVG Pattern (low contrast) -->
  <svg 
    aria-hidden="true" 
    class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full pointer-events-none z-10 w-[55vw]" 
    viewBox="0 0 800 1200" 
    preserveAspectRatio="xMaxYMin slice"
  >
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="hero-gradient" x1="0" x2="1">
        <stop offset="0" stop-color="white" stop-opacity="0.02"></stop>
        <stop offset="1" stop-color="#81171F" stop-opacity="0.02"></stop>
      </linearGradient>
    </defs>
    <rect x="0" y="0" width="800" height="1200" fill="url(#hero-gradient)"></rect>
  </svg>

  <!-- Content Container -->
  <div class="relative z-20 mx-auto text-center w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center max-w-3xl py-8 sm:py-12">
    
    <!-- Accent Line -->
    <div class="hero-accent mb-4 sm:mb-6 w-full" data-reveal>
      <span class="inline-block w-20 sm:w-28 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-200 to-burgundy-700 opacity-90"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Headline -->
    <h1 
      class="font-lora font-extrabold text-[clamp(3rem,6.5vw,4.6rem)] leading-[1.04] text-white" 
      id="hero-title"
      data-reveal
    >
      Menos Esforço. Mais Lucro.
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p 
      class="font-lora italic text-[clamp(1rem,3.6vw,1.8rem)] text-peach-300" 
      aria-describedby="hero-title"
      data-reveal
    >
      O mapa para a empreendedora que se recusa a escolher entre sucesso e liberdade.
    </p>

    <!-- Event Badge -->
    <div 
      class="hero-badge inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/6 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/12 px-3 py-1.5 mb-6 mt-6 text-neutral-200 text-[clamp(0.72rem,2.8vw,0.95rem)] shadow-[0_6px_30px_rgba(2,6,23,0.35)]" 
      role="img" 
      aria-label="Evento: 20 de Setembro, Lisboa Portugal, Mesa Corrida"
      data-reveal
    >
      <time datetime="2025-09-20">20 de Setembro</time>
      <span class="text-peach-300" aria-hidden="true">•</span>
      <span>Lisboa, Portugal</span>
      <span class="text-peach-300" aria-hidden="true">•</span>
      <em class="not-italic">Mesa Corrida</em>
    </div>

    <!-- Body Text -->
    <p 
      class="font-century text-white text-[clamp(1rem,3.2vw,1.125rem)] leading-relaxed max-w-[60ch] mx-auto mb-6 px-2"
      data-reveal
    >
      Um encontro presencial e intimista em Portugal para reestruturar o seu negócio, recuperar o seu tempo e multiplicar as vendas — sem burnout, com método. Um dia de imersão estratégica, ferramentas accionáveis e um plano de 90 dias para implementar mudanças reais.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Group -->
    <div 
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 mt-2 w-full sm:w-auto"
      data-reveal
    >
      <button 
        type="button"
        data-checkout-trigger
        data-source="hero"
        class="hero-cta-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 min-h-[48px] rounded-[14px] bg-gradient-to-r from-burgundy-700 to-navy-800 text-white font-bold shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(2,6,23,0.5)] transform-gpu transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-white/40 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-navy-900"
        aria-label="Garantir a minha vaga no evento"
        data-analytics-event="click_hero_cta"
      >
        Garantir a minha vaga
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>

      <a 
        href="#solucao" 
        class="text-white/90 underline underline-offset-4 text-sm sm:text-base transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-white" 
        data-analytics-event="click_hero_secondary"
      >
        Quero saber mais
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Limited Spots Notice -->
    <div 
      class="mt-6 text-xs text-white/70"
      role="status"
      aria-live="polite"
      data-reveal
    >
      Vagas limitadas — sessão com capacidade reduzida para garantir transformação.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll Indicator Button -->
  <button 
    class="hero-scroll-indicator absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-30 text-white/90 sm:block hidden bg-transparent border-none cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/40 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-navy-900" 
    id="scroll-indicator-btn" 
    aria-label="Role para baixo para ver mais conteúdo" 
    type="button"
    data-reveal
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1 w-full">
      <span class="font-lora text-xs">Role para baixo</span>
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </button>
</section>
<!-- Hero Section End -->


